The paper deals with wireless caching and physical layer security in wireless networks, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The focus on video streaming and backhaul capacity constraints suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and communication security (cs.CR). The use of optimization algorithms and complexity analysis points towards a possible association with data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
